Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.43,0:00:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.64,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.44,0:00:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.72,0:01:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.83,0:01:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.47,0:01:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.04,0:01:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殖民衛星派來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五部鋼彈的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.18,0:01:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是衛星反抗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.45,0:01:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈躲藏起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,避開聯合軍機動戰士部隊的耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以OZ為攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展開了各種作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.90,0:01:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ終於踏上歷史的表面舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.80,0:01:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,統帥特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.94,0:01:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以精銳的軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進行了消滅聯合軍的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派來地球的機動戰士和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.25,0:02:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的戰鬥令大地震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.59,0:02:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你當自己的生命是甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自爆!?別笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣自以為是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我之前也應該說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照感情行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人類正確的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.90,0:02:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十四話\N[01爆破指令]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.76,0:02:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好愛惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.17,0:03:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘇菲亞‧諾邊塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住在[馬賽]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的要由那裡開始嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來總算趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是陳列用的里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.97,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是聯合和OZ的主要軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.11,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.61,0:03:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何拘泥於機動戰士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.68,0:03:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巨大的機械會令人害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.31,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但同時會有強大的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用雙腳走路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是不喜歡以按鈕分勝負的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們喜歡像人類的戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.19,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人是無分形式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.39,0:03:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是\N那就是玩弄生命的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰爭中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.13,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死亡是更直接的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很少人知道OZ帶來的混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.67,0:04:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實全是羅姆斐拉財團的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.48,0:04:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團的聚會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在[雷門]郊外舉行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有很多賓客被邀請參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由歐洲的王侯貴族發起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用龐大財力和人面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直傾全力開發武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.76,0:04:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她向地球圈統一聯合軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提供機動戰士，擴張軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令今次政變得以成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.11,0:04:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法呢，因為我有很多前科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這扇門後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.85,0:04:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有殺死德利安氏\N和消滅妳王國的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.66,0:04:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.36,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日…!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為和平主義國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.40,0:05:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國的後裔\N我不會失禮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.34,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去，地球圈統一聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了世界和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我們尋求很多資金和援助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們毫不吝嗇\N盡力協助達成和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.35,0:05:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們變得想藉著對話尋求和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但地球有很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能用對話解決的紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類須要的\N不是受控制的局勢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且\N那以支配的形式得以實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣才能維持和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合無心支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配須要很大的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想逃避責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.68,0:05:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位擁有能支配時代的傳統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界因為幼小的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這等不完全的思想而墮落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.78,0:06:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要再次站出來的時刻來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.43,0:06:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ竟然想以這形式支配世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.36,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當他們隱藏在聯合之內時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.23,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團沒有表露這想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果聯合不能為世界帶來和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.37,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ就表明它的真正思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不繼續勝利\N支配制度就會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要勝利後有報酬才成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的支配制度的崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.52,0:06:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是對導致貧困的苛政的革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,參加了羅姆斐拉財團的國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.76,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算繼續不敗的戰爭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，他們需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最強的機動戰士部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是OZ的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.54,0:06:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈會戰勝OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.11,0:06:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ當鋼彈的性能是威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此，他們以直接攻擊衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令鋼彈束手無策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.35,0:07:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團想馬上消滅鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想藉很多人的犧牲\N君臨世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和希洛為了不產生犧牲者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想捨棄生命的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是難以明白的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我介紹率領OZ討伐聯合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且為了替世界帶來和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.20,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們奮勇戰鬥的騎士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.08,0:07:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團的一員兼OZ指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位或許認為OZ會以機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種軍事力量作出過份的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支配這詞語會令人聯想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壓制及專橫的暴政
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為這是抑制人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過度不必要的欲望的一種統治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.27,0:08:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神拋下人類不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.77,0:08:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類須要超越神的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無戰鬥的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超越了神的預測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.85,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種行為早晚會被神了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧，這裡不是我們來的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對以為戰爭是美好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說甚麼也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.24,0:08:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈一定會出現糾正那錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.11,0:08:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被漂亮話欺騙的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下!請停止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!我還有話要說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我求妳，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裡甚麼也解決不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦妳，路克蕾琪亞.諾茵特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，特列斯大人，失陪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是我邀請的朋友的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她剛才想說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.75,0:09:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她發覺到鋼彈令我們不安吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.63,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我們要有多點信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於那部鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是傑克斯‧馬吉斯也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.93,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太縱容區區一個駕駛員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞他在維多利亞基地修復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.10,0:09:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星派來的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部自爆了的鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.21,0:09:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然修理\N威脅我們的機動戰士!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他瘋了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為對衛星的警告也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為應該徹底破壞它!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很明白你們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然是財團的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就叫他馬上破壞鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.13,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的傳聞己經傳到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些大人物的耳裡了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈鑿成OZ的損失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是很大的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人看來是反對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能違背上頭的決定嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.88,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你答應破壞鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很活潑，嫌惡感也很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她知道多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的養父德利安氏臨終時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像對她說了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.56,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他告訴她你是山克王國出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個可以信賴的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有，你是唯一身處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在鋼彈01自爆地點的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你在修復鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以她認為那個駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.08,0:10:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯還生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是那駕駛員的名字嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.65,0:11:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下和他好像有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.42,0:11:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，多謝妳的報告，諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不向莉莉娜殿下\N表明身份嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能表明身份!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…重覆著染血歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的傑克斯‧馬吉斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，在這所大屋放火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.95,0:11:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把一切燒毀就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.15,0:11:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，神不會容許那種事發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為褻瀆神靈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許會受到懲罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.16,0:11:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，一定要作出懲罰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.06,0:11:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神是人類想像出來的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈統一聯合軍的\N諾邊塔元帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對作為制衡力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.89,0:12:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍事擴張抱有異議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使那是徒然也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他向地球各國及衛星提出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.16,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,裁軍甚至全面解除軍備的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.83,0:12:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ把那一日作為新時代的開幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓鋼彈擊落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔乘坐的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.44,0:12:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不認為這是和平的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元…元帥!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別衝動啊，年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這事件，世界或許永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.69,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法走到通向和平的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘇菲亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳快點離開這城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.94,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你擔心我，上尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.47,0:13:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們地球圈統一聯合\N的殘餘軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集結在馬賽這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.91,0:13:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ襲擊我們的行動越來越頻繁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以來，因為有聯合的基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.72,0:13:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以能守護這城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.06,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，現在基地會帶來危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡會成為戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我須要時間拋開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.77,0:13:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和爺爺在這裡生活的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.24,0:13:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔元帥是個偉大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.91,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一直希望有真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺過了身也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺的心願會留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會好好保存那心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘇菲亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.89,0:13:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上尉!敵襲!   OZ嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現10部艾亞利玆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們以為那麼少軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡就會被攻陷嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心，我們也不會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳快點去安全的地方，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.81,0:14:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別讓艾亞利玆進入居住區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎擊開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.82,0:14:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,里歐各自迎戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直是游擊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.07,0:14:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅敵人所有機動戰士\N繼續攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!我真大意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.29,0:14:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的里歐後退到地下水道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.26,0:15:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是主力部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亞利玆全體集合!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地下水道的里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰也想得出的方法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管我，現在的我礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.57,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以給OZ知道鋼彈的存在嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.48,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的部隊幾乎全軍覆沒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至此為止嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在地下水道!別落後!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘇菲亞‧諾邊塔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.49,0:16:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.76,0:16:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人艾亞利玆入侵下水道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,投降也沒用嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.47,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何會在這種地方?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亞利玆很快就會來到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!停止後退，迎擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.05,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.22,0:16:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能拖延很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我們要堅持到它的駕駛員回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.25,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要保護鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，它是最強的援軍!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.07,0:16:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續!別怕!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後…拜託你了…鋼彈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下水道的里歐全部被毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何會在這種地方!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要在通知其他人前收拾他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聯合和OZ的戰鬥裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我不會有任何感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N只是鋼彈不可以被看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.80,0:17:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部艾亞利玆被毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是奇蹟嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這部所屬不明的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是何方神聖也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在要感謝他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.01,0:18:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你叫希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.89,0:18:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是爺爺的墳墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.89,0:18:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要說的是甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.63,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死諾邊塔元帥的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我犯了錯而擊落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.10,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔元帥乘坐的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.74,0:18:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令他和很多祈求和平的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼…為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我只能這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.05,0:18:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘇菲亞‧諾邊塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是無可挽救的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,深愛元帥的親人的憤怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和元帥心有不甘的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.77,0:19:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望妳用那支槍令它們息怒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然想讓我這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你自己得到解脫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.14,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我只能這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卑鄙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太卑鄙了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.85,0:19:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳明白我不是來令妳難受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.09,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我去見妳的婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.93,0:19:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽聞她在[西西里亞]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.47,0:19:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由這裡開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.23,0:19:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所有親人面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為自己所犯的錯誤接受審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.60,0:19:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙所做的事好徹底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯所做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.58,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭是醜惡的自相殘殺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何…把它看成那麼漂亮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有這種生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈01爆破完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.55,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞哈特調查官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了，我可以收集碎片嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.46,0:20:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對我們提出的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有甚麼不滿意嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.23,0:20:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，我想親眼弄清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我要做一份令頑固的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.16,0:20:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉大人物認同的報告書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.24,0:20:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請隨便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.24,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有甚麼疑點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯‧馬吉斯也不是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輕易露出破綻的男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.12,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維多利亞基地沒有鋼彈的零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個喜愛機動戰士的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.12,0:21:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不會為了我們\N改變自己的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背叛羅姆斐拉財團\N對他有好處嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.43,0:21:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯的事我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團開始推動時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要巴結尊貴的資產階級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.07,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯的叛變就要是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個調查官想藉著找尋碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.98,0:21:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡量搏取羅姆斐拉財團的賞識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.32,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎樣找也不會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和資料不符的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.66,0:21:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要你和我一起演戲，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.79,0:21:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也只是覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.33,0:21:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅那部01好可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.06,0:21:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，托爾吉斯的後備零件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此幾乎完全沒有了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.34,0:21:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.54,0:21:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後不可大意令它受損了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒駕駛員能令傑克斯特校你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和托爾吉斯受損的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.61,0:22:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.46,0:22:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.71,0:22:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.71,0:22:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.71,0:22:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.71,0:22:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.21,0:22:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.71,0:23:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.21,0:23:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.71,0:23:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.71,0:23:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.00,0:23:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭應該是無情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但希洛把自己的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交託給諾邊塔夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.38,0:23:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯想以戰士身份決一死戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵邀請希洛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.35,0:23:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯在等候的南極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞哈特調查官的部隊追擊他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.19,0:23:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的再生將要留下新的火種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.02,0:23:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第十五話
